:','You can hide/display columns based on your needs and decide how many roles to list per screen using the Screen Options tab.'=>'You can hide/display columns based on your needs and decide how many roles to list per screen using the Screen Options tab.','You can filter the list of roles by types using the text links in the upper left. The default view is to show all roles.'=>'You can filter the list of roles by types using the text links in the upper left. The default view is to show all roles.','Hovering over a row in the roles list will display action links that allow you to manage your role. You can perform the following actions:'=>'Hovering over a row in the roles list will display action links that allow you to manage your role. You can perform the following actions:','<strong>Edit</strong> takes you to the editing screen for that role. You can also reach that screen by clicking on the role name.'=>'<strong>Edit</strong> takes you to the editing screen for that role. You can also reach that screen by clicking on the role name.','<strong>Delete</strong> removes your role from this list and permanently deletes it.'=>'<strong>Delete</strong> removes your role from this list and permanently deletes it.','<strong>Clone</strong> copies the role and takes you to the new role screen to further edit it.'=>'<strong>Clone</strong> copies the role and takes you to the new role screen to further edit it.','<strong>Users</strong> takes you to the users screen and lists the users that have that role.'=>'<strong>Users</strong> takes you to the users screen and lists the users that have that role.','You can permanently delete multiple roles at once. Select the roles you want to act on using the checkboxes, then select the action you want to take from the Bulk Actions menu and click Apply.'=>'You can permanently delete multiple roles at once. Select the roles you want to act on using the checkboxes, then select the action you want to take from the Bulk Actions menu and click Apply.','admin screenMembers'=>'Members','Roles and Capabilities'=>'Roles and Capabilities','Sidebar Widgets'=>'Sidebar Widgets','Private Site'=>'Private Site','Role Manager'=>'Role Manager','Capabilities'=>'Capabilities','Multiple User Roles'=>'Multiple User Roles','Enable Permissions'=>'Enable Permissions','Enable Private Site'=>'Enable Private Site','Disable Feed'=>'Disable Feed','Feed Error Message'=>'Feed Error Message','Your roles and capabilities will not revert back to their previous settings after deactivating or uninstalling this plugin, so use this feature wisely.'=>'Your roles and capabilities will not revert back to their previous settings after deactivating or uninstalling this plugin, so use this feature wisely.','Enable the role manager.'=>'Enable the role manager.','Denied capabilities should always overrule granted capabilities.'=>'Denied capabilities should always overrule granted capabilities.','Allow users to be assigned more than a single role.'=>'Allow users to be assigned more than a single role.','Enable the content permissions feature.'=>'Enable the content permissions feature.','Redirect all logged-out users to the login page before allowing them to view the site.'=>'Redirect all logged-out users to the login page before allowing them to view the site.','Show error message for feed items.'=>'Show error message for feed items.','Update Settings'=>'Update Settings','Role and Capabilities'=>'Role and Capabilities','Tick the checkbox for denied capabilities to always take precedence over granted capabilities when there is a conflict. This is only relevant when using multiple roles per user.'=>'Tick the checkbox for denied capabilities to always take precedence over granted capabilities when there is a conflict. This is only relevant when using multiple roles per user.','The role manager allows you to manage roles on your site by giving you the ability to create, edit, and delete any role. Note that changes to roles do not change settings for t